                                placerat. Etiam eu consequat lorem, id tempor elit. Aenean lobortis, ligula vitae
                                laoreet maximus, felis erat euismod dolor, mollis aliquet mi lacus rhoncus dolor. Sed
                                finibus urna sed sem bibendum placerat. Proin eu augue in felis pellentesque
                                sollicitudin nec id arcu. Nulla dui quam, auctor nec tristique vitae, sodales eget diam.
                                Nullam id accumsan sem, eu ornare eros. Nulla lobortis iaculis placerat. </h6>
                            <p><strong>Status:</strong> Rejected</p>
                            <p><strong>Uploaded:</strong> 12/15/2023 5:11PM</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


            <div class="col-md-5">
                <!-- Scrollable Document Section -->
                <div id="scrollable-section" class="scrollable-section" data-scroll-target="scrollableSection">
                    <div class="card mb-4 custom-card">
                        <div class="card h-100 shadow-xl">
                            <div class="card-header d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
                                <strong>Document Title</strong>
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                    <div class="mx-2 d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <twig:ux:icon name="tabler:pencil" class="icon-sm svg-icon me-1 icon-blue"
                                                      style="color: blue;"/>
                                        <span class="text-blue no-underline" style="cursor: pointer; color: blue;"
                                              onclick="window.location.href='list_document.html.twig'">Edit</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mx-2 d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <twig:ux:icon name="tabler:trash" class="icon-sm svg-icon me-1"
                                                      style="color: red;"/>
                                        <span class="text-red no-underline" style="cursor: pointer; color: red;"
                                              onclick="window.location.href='list_document.html.twig'">Delete</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <div class="col-auto">
                                        <twig:ux:icon name="tabler:file-type-pdf" class="icon-lg"/>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col">
